130 #ifndef __IO
131 #ifdef __cplusplus
132  #define __I volatile

135 #endif

144 #if !defined(REG_READ32)
145  #define REG_READ32(address) (*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))
146 #endif
147 
151 #if !defined(REG_WRITE32)
152  #define REG_WRITE32(address, value) ((*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))= (uint32_t)(value))
153 #endif
154 
158 #if !defined(REG_BIT_SET32)
159  #define REG_BIT_SET32(address, mask) ((*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))|= (uint32_t)(mask))
160 #endif
161 
165 #if !defined(REG_BIT_CLEAR32)
166  #define REG_BIT_CLEAR32(address, mask) ((*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))&= ((uint32_t)~((uint32_t)(mask))))
167 #endif
168 
173 #if !defined(REG_RMW32)
174  #define REG_RMW32(address, mask, value) (REG_WRITE32((address), ((REG_READ32(address)& ((uint32_t)~((uint32_t)(mask))))| ((uint32_t)(value)))))
175 #endif
